                    <div class="widget widget-menu-highlights">
                        <h3 class="font-large">Món ăn  nổi bật</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <div class="image"><img src="<%= url_for(" /assets/frontend/showcase/56x56.png ") %>" width="56" height="56" alt=""></div>
                                <h4 class="title"><a href="" title="">French Wedge</a></h4>
                                <div class="excerpt">
                                    <p>Suspendisse dictu m suscipit odio. Nulla dui arcu, fermentum quis, mattis quis, ultricies. </p>
